    <summary>Terminal file transfer client and dual-pane file manager for SCP, SFTP, FTP, SMB, S3, WebDAV and Kubernetes.</summary>
    <description>
EasySCP is a terminal file transfer client and dual-pane file manager for SCP,
SFTP, FTP/FTPS, SMB/CIFS, S3, WebDAV and Kubernetes. It runs on Windows, macOS,
Linux and BSD.

Core features:

- Dual-pane local and remote file explorer
- File operations including create, remove, rename, search, view and edit
- Bookmarks and recent connections
- SSH key and username/password authentication for SFTP and SCP
- External editor integration
- Configurable themes, explorer format, editor and sorting
- Password storage through the operating system key vault where available
    </description>
